<tr>
    <td>
        <p>
            We received a request to reset your password for your Wordhive
            account. We understand the importance of account security, and
            we're here to assist you.
        </p>
        <p>
            To proceed with the password reset, please use the One-Time
            Password (OTP) below:
        </p>
    </td>
</tr>

<tr align="center">
    <td style="padding: 28px 0">
        {{#each code}}
        <span style="
                    background-color: #ccebff;
                    font-weight: 600;
                    padding: 8px 16px;
                    margin: 0 10px;
                    border-radius: 0.5rem;
                  ">
            {{this}}
        </span>
        {{/each}}
    </td>
</tr>

<tr>
    <td>
        <p>
            Please note that this OTP is only valid for a maximum of 15
            minutes.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you didn't initiate this password reset request, please
            ignore this email. Rest assured that your account is secure.
        </p>
        <p>
            For any further questions or concerns, please reach out to our
            support team. We're here to assist you in any way we can.
        </p>
        <p>
            Thank you for being a valued member of the Wordhive community.
        </p>
    </td>
</tr>